parameters.name: Headers
parameters.description: By default, prefetch requests include the Accept-Encoding:gzip header. If you want a prefetch request to include other headers or implement multi-replica prefetch, you can specify a custom prefetch header by configuring the Headers parameter.

parameters.name: SiteId
parameters.description: The website ID. You can call the [ListSites](~~2850189~~) operation to obtain the ID.
